The Barclays golf tournament was
shortened to 54 holes from 72 because of the threat of Hurricane
Irene, the PGA Tour said in a press release.  The tournament is being played at Plainfield County Club in
Edison,  New Jersey . The hurricane is forecast to move into that
area on Sunday, when the final 18 holes were scheduled to be
played.  It is the first tournament in the PGA Tourâ€™s Playoffs for
